quran[20{c,v,t}:
26,20,"moose ne jawab diya"" uss waqt woh kaam mein ne nadanstgi mein kar diya tha"
26,21,phir mein tumahray khauf se bhaag gaya is ke baad mere rab ne mujh ko hukum ataa kya aur mujhe Rasolo-n mein shaamil kar liya
26,22,"raha tera ahsaan jo to ne mujh par jataayaa hai to is ki haqeeqat yeh hai ke to ne bani Israel ko ghulam bana liya tha """
26,23,"firaon ne kaha"" aur yeh rab alameen kya hota hai? """
26,24,"moose ne jawab diya"" aasman aur zameen ka rab, aur unn sab cheezon ka rab jo aasman aur zameen ke darmain hain, agar tum yaqeen laane walay ho """
26,25,"firaon ne apne gird o paish ke logon se kaha"" suntay ho? """
26,26,"moose ne kaha"" tumhara rab bhi aur tumahray un aaba o ajdaad ka rab bhi jo guzar chuke hain """
26,27,"firaon ne ( hazreen se ) kaha"" tumahray yeh rasool sahib jo tumhari taraf beje gay hain, bilkul hi pagal maloom hotay hain """
26,28,"moose ne kaha"" mashriq o maghrib aur jo kuch un ke darmain hai sab ka rab, agar aap log kuch aqal rakhtay hain """
26,29,"firaon ne kaha"" agar to ne mere siwa kisi aur ko mabood banaya to tujhe mein unn logon mein shaamil kar dun ga jo qaid khaanoon mein parre sarr rahay hain """
26,30,"moose ne kaha"" agarchay mein le aon tairay samnay aik Sarih cheez bhi? """
26,31,"firaon ne kaha"" acha to le aa agar to sacha hai """
26,32,( is ki zabaan se yeh baat nikaltay hi ) moose ne apna asa phenka aur yakayak woh aik Sarih asdeha tha
26,33,phir uss ne apna haath ( baghal se ) khincha aur woh sab dekhnay walon ke samnay chamak raha tha
26,34,"firaon apne gird o paish ke sardaro se bola"" yeh shakhs yaqeenan aik maahir jadugar hai"
26,35,"chahta hai ke apne jaadoo ke zor se tum ko malik se nikaal day ab batao tum kya hukum dete ho? """
26,36,"unhon ne kaha"" usay aur is ke bhai ko rok lijiye aur shehron mein hrkare bhaij degiye"
26,37,"ke har syane jadugar ko aap ke paas le ayen """
26,38,chunancha aik roz muqarrar waqt par jadugar ikathay kar liye gay
26,39,"aur logon se kaha gaya"" tum ijtima mein chalo ge ?"
